{"tid":2462151,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登：不尋求與中國對抗 但會問責台港議題","createTime":"2021-03-25T23:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T00:55:11.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"77585579e97483f6cab20a9a730e648d527bc087","tid":2462151,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:33:50.000Z","msg":"（中央社記者江今葉華盛頓25日專電）美國總統拜登今天表示，美國並不尋求與中國對抗，但要求中國必須遵守國際規範，公平競爭。美國會繼續在新疆、香港等議題發聲，也會針對南海、台灣等議題向中國問責。<br />\n<br />\n在上任2個多月後，拜登（Joe Biden）今天終於召開任內首場記者會<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n談及美中關係，拜登首先花了不少時間暢談他跟中國國家主席習近平的私交。他表示，他跟習近平兩人在分別擔任副總統與副主席時就有過多次詳細、直率的私下對談。<br />\n<br />\n拜登形容習近平骨子裡沒有民主，但是個聰明的人。習近平和俄羅斯總統蒲亭（Vladimir Putin）一樣，認為專制是未來的潮流，在日益複雜的世界裡，民主無法發揮作用。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n此外，拜登提到透過民主國家共同合作，明確表達不論是南海或是台灣等議題，都會向中國問責，並要求中國遵守國際規範。美國重視自由、人權，不會坐視中國持續迫害人權，也不會對新疆維吾爾族、香港發生的事噤聲。<br />\n<br />\n拜登表示，美中之間存在激烈的競爭關係，中國的總體目標在成為世界的領導者、最富裕與最強大的國家，但這不會發生，因為美國將繼續成長與壯大。（編輯：徐崇哲）1100326<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103260007.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202103260007.aspx&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GoeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=b061521f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103260007.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"048fcd596c0b3f5c28d9b1130313576d0484d2da","tid":2462151,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:37:17.000Z","msg":"佢比侵侵更出色，聯西反中"},{"pid":"88febf7ec6965fefbc7739986769a86d44a35d73","tid":2462151,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:37:21.000Z","msg":"但習近平要同成個西方世界對抗呢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/commentaries/wp/COM-10252017065035.html/com1025.png/@@images/0e6b7029-2a93-4881-9752-ea2188f7522a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fcommentaries%2Fwp%2FCOM-10252017065035.html%2Fcom1025.png%2F%40%40images%2F0e6b7029-2a93-4881-9752-ea2188f7522a.png&h=78ee6073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/japgunping.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F04%2Fjapgunping.png&h=6eaa5788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/IKBm0ok1GQg/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FIKBm0ok1GQg%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=c9fd5947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0mT7OHjI7dM/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F0mT7OHjI7dM%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=8abb63ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73098c38ea785616c6b7a0522dc3f0643778e3e1","tid":2462151,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:39:02.000Z","msg":"「發聲」"},{"pid":"6e113b4e8df901033a21eb8313fe0812ee101a29","tid":2462151,"uid":380132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:46:28.000Z","msg":"歡迎習大大打柒美國"},{"pid":"df863848815b103df58b954a4b1b3e5ed370f61e","tid":2462151,"uid":184249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:55:11.000Z","msg":"已訓斥"}]}